<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(الْمَسْأَلَة الْحَادِيَة وَالْعشْرُونَ:)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الْمُتَيَمم إِذا رأى المَاء فِي خلال صلَاته <span class="c2">(كَا)</span> :<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الْمَذْهَب:</span> لَا تبطل صلَاته.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">عِنْدهم:</span> تبطل.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الدَّلِيل من الْمَنْقُول:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">لنا:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قَوْله تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{يَا أَيهَا الَّذين آمنُوا إِذا قُمْتُم إِلَى الصَّلَاة}</span> ... الْآيَة.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَجه الدَّلِيل:</span> أَنه أَمر بِالتَّيَمُّمِ للصَّلَاة، كَمَا أَمر بِالْغسْلِ، وَقد أَتَى بِهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">لَهُم:</span> ... .<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>